rder-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/convert/hashtag-generator\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Text Tools</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold\">Hashtag Generator</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Free Gemini-powered AI generation with three generations per day and no account required.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/convert/text-case-converter\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Text Tools</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold\">Text Case Converter</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Convert text to uppercase, lowercase, title case, sentence case or slug case.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/convert/watermark-image\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Image Tools</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold\">Watermark Image</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Add text watermark to images online for free. Protect JPG, PNG and WEBP images instantly.</p></a></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 pb-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl border-l-4 border-emerald-400 bg-emerald-400/5 p-7\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-black\">Explore all free AI tools</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-300\">Use three free Gemini generations per day across writing and social media tools. No account or API key is required.</p><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\" href=\"/ai-tools\">Browse Free AI Tools</a></div></section><section class=\"px-6 pb-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl\"><aside class=\"rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 p-6\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase text-amber-200\">Sponsored</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-white\">Featured software partner</h3><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400\">A reserved placement for a relevant file, productivity or document software partner.</p><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-amber-200 hover:text-amber-100\" href=\"/partners\">Explore partnership options</a></aside></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-white/10 bg-slate-900/40 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black\">Why use these tools?</h2><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 leading-7 text-slate-300\">Generate tailored starting points with real AI rather than fixed templates.</p><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 leading-7 text-slate-300\">Refine every Gemini-generated result for your audience, platform and brand voice.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black\">Frequently asked questions</h2><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Do I need an API key?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">No. A2ZConvertor uses its backend Gemini connection and does not ask users for provider keys.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Do I need an account?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">No account is required for the free daily allowance.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Is free AI unlimited?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">No. Free generation has a daily allowance to control costs and availability.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">What happens at the daily limit?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Try again tomorrow or support A2ZConvertor to help fund higher free limits.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Which AI model is used?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">The public tools use the owner-configured Gemini model.</p></div></div><h2 class=\"mt-16 text-2xl font-black\">Explore other categories</h2><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/pdf-tools\">PDF Tools</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/video-tools\">Video Tools</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/audio-tools\">Audio Tools</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/text-tools\">Text Tools</a><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\" href=\"/tools\">Browse all tools</a></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-12 max-w-7xl\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><div class=\"\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-black\">Get new free tools and productivity tips.</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-7 text-slate-400\">Be first to know when we launch new converters, PDF tools and browser-based productivity tools.</p><form class=\"mt-5 flex gap-3 flex-col\"><label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"_R_35bsnlb_\">Email address</label><input id=\"_R_35bsnlb_\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" class=\"min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-xl